      <title>商务部长表示中国寻求加强与新西兰在CPTPP方面的合作</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-seeks-strengthen-cooperation-with-new-zealand-cptpp-commerce-minister-says-2024-02-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国商务部长表示，中方愿同新方在加入《全面且进步的跨太平洋伙伴关系协定》进程中继续加强合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-seeks-strengthen-cooperation-with-new-zealand-cptpp-commerce-minister-says-2024-02-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 23:40:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国财长称企业改革计划将继续下去，直至“韩国折扣”问题得到解决</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-finmin-says-corporate-reform-plan-continue-until-korea-discount-is-2024-02-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国财政部长表示，政府的企业改革计划将继续分步骤进行，直至当地股市的“韩国贴价”问题得到解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-finmin-says-corporate-reform-plan-continue-until-korea-discount-is-2024-02-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 23:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾盟友图瓦卢周一任命新总理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tuvalu-name-new-prime-minister-monday-2024-02-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位官员表示，图瓦卢周一上午将宣布一位新总理，预计该总理将在没有受到该太平洋岛国立法者反对的情况下当选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tuvalu-name-new-prime-minister-monday-2024-02-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 22:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔利班释放在阿富汗关押的奥地利极右翼活动人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taliban-releases-austrian-far-right-activist-held-afghanistan-2024-02-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔利班周日释放了去年 5 月在阿富汗被捕的 84 岁奥地利人、极右民族主义者赫伯特·弗里茨 (Herbert Fritz)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taliban-releases-austrian-far-right-activist-held-afghanistan-2024-02-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 17:18:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>文件显示，印度尼西亚可能扩大财政赤字以资助免费学校午餐</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-may-widen-fiscal-deficit-fund-free-school-lunch-document-shows-2024-02-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社周日看到的一份简报文件显示，印度尼西亚可能不得不扩大预算赤字，以资助可能的新总统普拉博沃·苏比安托(Prabowo Subianto)承诺的数十亿美元的免费学校午餐计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-may-widen-fiscal-deficit-fund-free-school-lunch-document-shows-2024-02-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 16:53:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称已在金门附近海域进行巡逻</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-has-conducted-patrols-waters-near-kinmen-2024-02-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国海警局称，2月25日，中国福建海警在金门附近海域进行巡逻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-has-conducted-patrols-waters-near-kinmen-2024-02-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 08:10:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理承诺野火摧毁房屋时提供“一切支持”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/australian-homes-destroyed-bushfires-extreme-heat-ahead-2024-02-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·艾博内塞周日承诺，将提供一切所需的支持，以协助维多利亚州应对长达数天的山火紧急情况，这场山火已将房屋夷为平地，此前当局警告本周极端高温可能会加剧火势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/australian-homes-destroyed-bushfires-extreme-heat-ahead-2024-02-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 02:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>岛上营地火灾造成八名罗兴亚难民受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fire-island-camp-injures-eight-rohingya-refugees-2024-02-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方称，周六，偏远的巴桑查尔岛一处营地因煤气泄漏而引发火灾，八名罗兴亚难民受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fire-island-camp-injures-eight-rohingya-refugees-2024-02-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 09:17:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京承诺再提供 49 亿美元帮助台积电扩大日本产量</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tokyo-pledges-further-49-bln-help-tsmc-expand-japan-production-2024-02-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本表示，将向台积电额外提供高达 7320 亿日元（48.6 亿美元）的补贴，帮助其建设第二家芯片制造厂，周六这家台湾公司标志着其第一家日本工厂的开业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tokyo-pledges-further-49-bln-help-tsmc-expand-japan-production-2024-02-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 08:48:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国前总理他信身体虚弱，拘留释放后“很高兴”——总理斯雷塔</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-pm-says-ex-premier-thaksin-still-weak-after-release-detention-2024-02-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维信（Srettha Thavisin）周六表示，前总理他信·西那瓦（Thaksin Shinawatra）很高兴，心情很好，但在最近从医院释放后仍然很虚弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-pm-says-ex-premier-thaksin-still-weak-after-release-detention-2024-02-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 07:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
